In IndexedDB externs http://closure-compiler.googlecode.com/svn/trunk/externs/w3c_indexeddb.js

IDBRequest object must have error value according to http://www.w3.org/TR/IndexedDB/#idl-def-IDBRequest

Add 


/**
 * @type {!DOMError}
 * @const
 */
IDBRequest.prototype.error;
